caption:
Rooted in change. 

Last year, ILIA announced an ongoing partnership with 1% for the Planet and @onetreeplanted. Our goal: to plant 1 million trees in the Amazon rainforest by the end of 2023. 

To reach this milestone, we’ve committed 1% of sales from our bestselling Super Serum Skin Tint SPF 40 to tackle deforestation—one of the greatest threats to our planet today. 

This year, we're zeroing in on the Peruvian Amazon, where we're pledging 580,000 trees to help sustain local communities—and the lungs of the world. 

Thank you for joining the reforestation movement.

caption:
Break the cycle. 

A less-than-glowing reality of the beauty industry—most makeup components are too small to be recycled. We want better, so we’ve partnered with Pact Collective, an NGO which recycles the hard-to-recycle and gives used beauty packaging a cleaner future. 

Tap the link in bio to receive a label, and we’ll take back up to 10 empties (even from other brands) and recycle them responsibly through Pact. 

Because little by little, a little becomes a lot. #EarthWeek
